text: Israa-iil xayloh Ambiyah Raatal Maryam baxa Nabii Qiisa katasneeh Rubne kaak naharat yemeete tawraat kitab Nummaysak, Nabii Qiisah injiil kitab necee Baditik (maxqawitik) tirtooy Yallih madqooqih Baxxaqqa kay addal anuk, kaak foocat yemeete tawraat kitab usuk Yallih xaquk yaniimih Sumaaqitak yemeete, Yallak meesita marah tirtoo kee kassis yakke kitab kaa abne
